data.description: Stunning Updated 3BD/2BA Ranch! Open floor plan with a beautifully updated kitchen that has custom cabinets, 15 foot granite island/bar, stainless steel appliances and a 5 burner gas range with vent hood.  The living room has a gas fireplace that boasts a granite mantle. Lots of unique lighting throughout the home.  Both bathrooms have been updated with subway tile and the primary en-suite has a towel warmer.  Windows and water heater were installed in 2018. Conveniently located to beaches, shopping and amazing restaurants. Trantwood Elementary, Great Neck Middle and Cox High School District.  VA assumable 2.6% interest rate for VA buyer.  Ask listing agent for details.This home has it all!
